"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"10db03",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Baseline genotype for protease inhibitor, nonnucleoside RTI, nucleoside/nucleotide RTI mutations for persons who have never initiated therapy, are reengaging in care and not receiving therapy, or with inconsistent access to therapy. INSTI genotype is recommended only if suspicion for INSTI mutation transmission."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
